{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"16251d98-9643-4737-b52c-198f77e7b73c","content":"Good news — with .NET 10 SDK, `dotnet test` **natively supports MTP**. The `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property was the .NET 9 opt-in flag and is **no longer needed**. The SDK automatically detects that your project is MTP-enabled (via `EnableMSTestRunner`) and routes through the new test infrastructure.\n\nYou can safely remove it:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_vqKXs319nqGCzAwg8kn1wS","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Removing obsolete MTP property"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"tooluse_M7vemhojkJrBodzs54nBmg","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-61ae3dce269149bc9cf12ce9272b16cf/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-61ae3dce269149bc9cf12ce9272b16cf/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"5f5e2f37-8174-4b15-982d-ad10a4bb39f7","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is on .NET 10 SDK and wants to know about native MTP support. Let me explain what changed in .NET 10.\n\nIn .NET 10, `dotnet test` has native Microsoft Testing Platform (MTP) integration. The key change is:\n\n1. .NET 10 SDK ships with native MTP support in `dotnet test` — it can directly invoke MTP-based test executables without the VSTest bridge.\n2. You no longer need `<TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>` — that property was needed in .NET 9 to opt into the preview MTP integration. In .NET 10, MTP is the default when the test project is an MTP project (i.e., has `EnableMSTestRunner`).\n\n\n3. The .NET 10 SDK automatically detects MTP-enabled projects, so you can simply remove that property if you had it set for .NET 9 compatibility.","outputTokens":612,"requestId":"BD00:2CA3BD:1DA7F6C:215BA72:6A07C568"},"id":"0c3707f7-46c4-4c3d-b345-1d2f0349f725","timestamp":"2026-05-16T01:16:34.668Z","parentId":"bcdb40b7-6b01-4960-9e4e-4beddfcf0957"}
